@node INTRO "Introduction"
@toc    Main
        @{i}Briscola v1.0  ©1996 by Fabio Lopiano - lopiano@infoservizi.it@{ui}


@{b}Briscola @{ub}(in English: Trump) is a traditional italian card game. 
It is played with a @{"40 cards deck" link CARDS} between two or four players.
In this version of the game it is only possible to play in two, human versus 
computer.

The @{"rules" link RULES} are easy and a good memory is needed to play well
of course this is not a problem for the computer player ;)

The game has been tested on an Amiga 1200 and it should work on any Amiga with
at least WorkBench 2.0.

@endnode

